comments: Adams (NOP) briefly grasps Noel's (NYK) arm during Bledsoe's (NOP) driving shot attempt but Adams immediately removes his hand. The contact that occurs is marginal.
Randle (NYK) establishes himself in a legal position in Ingram's (NOP) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the pick.
Ball (NOP) holds Noel's (NYK) arm during the rebound and the contact affects his FOM.
Ball (NOP) makes contact to Noel's (NYK) head during his shot attempt near the rim.
Randle (NYK) makes contact with the ball and he dislodges it from Williamson (NOP).
Ball (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position during Quickley's (NYK) drive.
Ball (NOP) extends his forearm into Quickley (NYK) and the contact dislodges him during the loose ball.
Randle (NYK) makes contact to Ingram's (NOP) arm that affect his FOM.
Rose (NYK) commits a take foul on Bledsoe (NOP).
Rose (NYK) legally contests Bledsoe's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
